age_band_analysis.description: Pass rates by vehicle age compared to national averages. Positive vs_national values indicate above-average performance for that age band.

age_bands.3-7 years: New vehicles - most pass easily, limited differentiation
age_bands.8-10 years: Maturing - issues start emerging, meaningful comparisons
age_bands.18-20 years: Veteran - notable longevity, sample caveats apply
age_bands.21+ years: Classic - very small samples, often collector vehicles

make_performance.methodology: Pass rates compared to national average for vehicles of the same age. Positive vs_national indicates above-average performance for that age band.
